OL,3,CChinese retail giant launches in UK
OL,4,Cwith new Joybuy business
OL,6,FChinese online retail giant JD.com is
OL,7,Flaunching in the UK through its new
OL,8,FJoybuy platform, as it seeks to target
OL,9,Fbargain-hunting British shoppers.
OL,11,FThe #30 billion ecommerce firm is
OL,12,Flaunching the shopping platform on
OL,13,FMonday, as it seeks to challenge major
OL,14,Frivals including Amazon in the UK.
OL,16,FThe move comes after US and Hong-Kong
OL,17,Flisted JD.com pulled out of talks for
OL,18,Ftwo separate deals to buy major UK
OL,19,Fretail brands over the past two years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
