OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773626592
OL,3,CChinese retail giant launches in UK
OL,4,Cwith new Joybuy business
OL,6,FIn 2024, the group abandoned plans for
OL,7,Fa possible deal to buy Currys, and
OL,8,Flast September it walked away from
OL,9,Ftalks over a potential takeover of
OL,10,FArgos from Sainsbury's.
OL,12,FThe group is now going to challenge
OL,13,Fboth retail brands, among many others,
OL,14,Fwith its launch.
OL,16,FChina's largest retailer will offer
OL,17,Fproducts across technology,
OL,18,Fappliances, beauty, home, groceries
OL,19,Fand other essentials.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
