OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773626592
OL,3,CChinese retail giant launches in UK
OL,4,Cwith new Joybuy business
OL,6,FIt said it will also offer next-day
OL,7,Fdelivery to about 17 million
OL,8,Fhouseholds across the UK from its
OL,9,Flaunch after establishing its own
OL,10,Flogistics operations.
OL,12,FThe group will run distribution sites
OL,13,Ffrom Milton Keynes and Luton to help
OL,14,Fdeliver significant scope from the
OL,15,Fstart of its operations in the UK.
OL,17,FBosses said the business plans to
OL,18,Festablish itself in the UK for "a long
OL,19,Ftime" and believes a combination of
OL,20,Fits product range, value and
OL,21,Fconvenience will entice new customers.
