OL,3,CChinese retail giant launches in UK
OL,4,Cwith new Joybuy business
OL,6,F"We are here for a long time, as our
OL,7,FCEO has said," he told the Press
OL,8,FAssociation.
OL,10,F"We have spent a lot of time working
OL,11,Fand honing to get our web and app
OL,12,Fproposition right, making it work in
OL,13,Fbeta testing over the time.
OL,15,F"We have to make sure the customer
OL,16,Fexperience is really great."
