OL,3,CChinese retail giant launches in UK
OL,4,Cwith new Joybuy business
OL,6,FThe company is simultaneously
OL,7,Flaunching into six new European
OL,8,Fmarkets, which include Germany, the
OL,9,FNetherlands, France, Belgium and
OL,10,FLuxembourg.
OL,12,FThe business struck a 2.2 billion euro
OL,13,F(#1.9 billion) deal to snap up Germany-
OL,14,Fbased electronics retail group
OL,15,FCeconomy last year.
